{"tid":504176,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)魔鬼屍餐1-3","createTime":"2017-12-19T15:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T05:19:32.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1a23fe7f90fc04d936493d860e22d7af46e50e08","tid":504176,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T15:46:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=FFJHfFyzXKEE2yn2KHul8lKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=73d9b32e\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=FFJHfFyzXKEE2yn2KHul8lKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=e5e6feb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3442/3978854159_e0c9c9a0f1_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarm4.static.flickr.com%2F3442%2F3978854159_e0c9c9a0f1_o.jpg&h=53e770c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.姐姐特麗薩和弟弟達瑞就讀於一所離家很遠的學校。一個陽光明媚的春日，因放春假而得以回家度假的姐弟倆開著輛破車興高采烈地行駛在空無一人的鄉間公路上。突然，一輛老式改裝卡車超車時差點將他們擠下路基。不久，他們又突然發現那輛車停在離公路不遠的一座廢棄的教堂旁，一個穿著寬大雨衣戴著寬邊帽子的大個子似乎在往一個很深很深的管子里扔屍體似的東西，於是達瑞決定讓姐姐打電話報警，大個子似乎發現了他們，馬上駕車飛速撞向他們..<br />\n<br />\n2.班諾高中的籃球隊員和啦啦隊員搭著校車正要趕一場比賽，沒想到校車卻在荒郊野外的高速公路上爆胎，教練發現輪胎被一個古老的星型鑣刀刺破。這時傑克在他弟弟被擄走的事發地點也發現了一個古老的利刃。 夜越來越深，困在半路上的教練和學生，打算向外界求救卻發現手機沒格無線電無人回應，荒郊野外求救無門，在逼不得已的情況下，他們只好用剩下的三個輪胎冒險上路，可是沒多久另外一把飛來的利刃又把輪胎刺破，使得全車的人不得不下車一探究竟........<br />\n<br />\n3.Trish Jenner（第一部女主）現在已經是一個十幾歲大孩子的媽媽，他孩子叫Darry，以她23年前失去的弟弟為名。Trish最近經常發惡夢，看到她兒子重複遭遇到她弟弟被那隻怪物殺害的命運。為了確保惡夢不再重現。Trish利用她現在擁有的金錢和能力決定與老、少Jack（第二部的老爺子和他兒子）完成最終的任務，徹底消除蝙蝠人的恐怖陰影<br />\n<br />\n12 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=FFJHfFyzXKEE2yn2KHul8lKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=9608fe22\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=FFJHfFyzXKEE2yn2KHul8lKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=2031849f\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e68a88c105fe2cb2d1b0c6d45f3727392f1469e","tid":504176,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77db01d5003a208c7cfd170fef10760b38e872be","tid":504176,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c229fe1c48af892cfa1a9587055d2bdbf85614eb","tid":504176,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3174580427135aee215301a1c5ce50a8f8f6dbca","tid":504176,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci